wiki.summary: "Can't Feel My Face" is the 7th track on the album Beauty Behind the Madness released under the artist The Weeknd. The song is sung and performed by Canadian singer, Abel Tesfaye. The song was written and produced by Max Martin and Ali Payami with additional songwriting from Savan Kotecha, Abel Tesfaye (The Weeknd) and Peter Svensson. The song went number 1 in the charts of Australia (ARIA), Canada, Denmark, Iceland, New Zealand, South Africa and The US (Billboard Hot 100). Read more on Last.fm.
